# Nevernotbecoming — the COMPLETE bee transmission, sung.
#
# Every word of the text, framed by its own bzzzz (a vocoded /z/
# cluster on a low Em stack — the choir literally buzzes). Verses are
# the legible Talker on the scored pitch line (one strophic tune:
# E4-G4-A4 rise, B4 peak, F#4-E4 fall; breaths at the commas). "All
# concepts of self as separate dissolve..." is a rising PRE-CHORUS;
# the chorus is the full egregore sentence in 20-band vocoder chords
# with gliding voicings; paragraph five is a low recitative bridge
# over a bass pedal with the pads thinned to the tenor alone;
# "abeeing" holds its pun, "nevernotbecoming" takes the B4->F#5
# ascent; the last verse settles home and the choir exhales one
# final aaah before the buzz recedes.
#
# Pads: slow counterpoint (common tones hold, steps melt at 2.5-4
# s/octave, suspensions resolve mid-chord). Mixed by measurement:
# vox_level rides to 2 in choir spans (the band vocoder's tanh caps
# its own output), pads duck under the choir, bass at gain 2.
#
# Form (beats): intro 16 (buzz 8) | V1-3 48 | V4-7 64 | PRE 16 |
#   CH 36 | aaah 8 | V8-11 64 | PRE 16 | CH 36 | bridge 48 |
#   OUT 36 | FIN 36 | aaah 12 | bzzz 8 | tail 8   = 452

bpm 100
gate 1

automate vox_clarity
  1
automate vox_level
  0.9 R:8 2:0.2 R:7.8 0.9:0.2 R:111.8 2:0.2 R:59.8 0.9:0.2 R:63.8 2:0.2 R:51.8 0.9:0.2 R:119.8 2:0.2 R:19.8 0.9:0.2 R:7.6
automate vox_mode
  2 R:8 1:0.2 R:7.8 2:0.2 R:111.8 1:0.2 R:59.8 2:0.2 R:63.8 1:0.2 R:51.8 2:0.2 R:119.8 1:0.2 R:19.8 2:0.2 R:7.6
automate vox_dry
  0.5 R:8 0.15:0.2 R:7.8 0.5:0.2 R:111.8 0.15:0.2 R:59.8 0.5:0.2 R:63.8 0.15:0.2 R:51.8 0.5:0.2 R:119.8 0.15:0.2 R:19.8 0.5:0.2 R:7.6
automate reverb_wet
  0.2 R:128 0.3:1 R:59 0.2:1 R:63 0.3:1 R:51 0.2:1 R:119 0.32:1 R:26.4
automate reverb_decay
  0.6 R:128 0.75:1 R:59 0.6:1 R:63 0.75:1 R:51 0.6:1 R:119 0.72:1 R:26.4
automate tape_drive
  0.15
automate tape_age
  0.3

# ---- the voice -------------------------------------------------------
