automate choir.glide
  1.2

# The third voice of the pre-chorus trio: inner-voice steps, then one
# leap of a fifth on 'dissolve' — paid for with a stepwise descent
track third vox vel=1 len=1
  R:128
  C4:2 D4:2 C4:1 G4:3 F#4:2 E4:2 F#4:2 G#4:2
  R:108
  C4:2 D4:2 C4:1 G4:3 F#4:2 E4:2 F#4:2 G#4:2
  R:184

