  1 R:8 2:0.2 R:7.8 1:0.2 R:111.8 2:0.2 R:59.8 1:0.2 R:63.8 2:0.2 R:51.8 1:0.2 R:119.8 2:0.2 R:19.8 1:0.2 R:7.6
